```

Override `Equals` (used for plan caching/dedup) and `Copy` (defined in the .cpp). For jq this would hold the filter string and ideally the parsed jq program.

**`/Users/tim_vergenz/code/personal/duckdb-jq/duckdb/src/function/scalar/string/regexp.cpp:79`** — the actual `bind_scalar_function_t`:

```cpp
unique_ptr<FunctionData> RegexpMatchesBind(ClientContext &context, ScalarFunction &bound_function,
                                           vector<unique_ptr<Expression>> &arguments) {
    D_ASSERT(arguments.size() == 2 || arguments.size() == 3);
    RE2::Options options;
    options.set_log_errors(false);
    string constant_string;
